      <title>智利部长称Codelco铜产量受到致命事故影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/codelco-copper-output-affected-by-fatal-accident-chile-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利国有公司 Codelco 正在努力保住全球最大铜供应商的头衔，该公司在其一座矿山发生致命事故后，由于运营恢复缓慢，产量预计将下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/codelco-copper-output-affected-by-fatal-accident-chile-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 22:35:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市将因美联储鹰派言论而下跌：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[强劲的经济数据和鹰派的美联储言论强化了利率将在更长时间内保持较高水平的猜测，美国股市和国债延续本月的抛售，亚洲股市预计将下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 22:18:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥官员表示，刺激上市的规则草案即将准备就绪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/draft-rules-to-spur-listings-nearly-ready-mexico-official-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥财政部副部长加布里埃尔·约里奥表示，墨西哥正在对刺激更多债务和股票上市所需的法规草案进行最后修改，这是立法者去年通过的改革目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/draft-rules-to-spur-listings-nearly-ready-mexico-official-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 22:10:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国旨在结束困扰其股市的泡沫时代</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/china-aims-to-end-age-of-froth-that-has-plagued-its-stock-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国正在寻求通过在其十年一次的资本市场改革计划中转向价值投资，来结束投机者驱动的盛衰交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/china-aims-to-end-age-of-froth-that-has-plagued-its-stock-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
